<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Learn More</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="bg-gray-900 border-b border-white/10">
      <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-6 flex justify-between items-center"
      >
        <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-400">Guide</a>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="text-sm font-medium text-white hover:text-indigo-400"
        >
          ‚Üê Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <main
      class="flex-grow px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-gray-300 space-y-6"
    >
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-400 mb-4">
        Learn More About Our Project
      </h1>

      <p>
        This app is built to help learners discover the best tutorials,
        playlists, and video resources from YouTube, filtered and ranked
        intelligently using view counts, likes, comment sentiment, and more.
      </p>

      <p>
        We use YouTube's official API to gather content, apply smart scoring
        algorithms, cache results for performance, and give you fast access to
        high-quality content without distractions.
      </p>

      <p>
        Currently, we support local and Google-based authentication. Logged-in
        users get higher search limits, saved search history (coming soon), and
        personalized features in the future.
      </p>

      <div
        class="border-l-4 border-indigo-500 pl-4 text-sm italic text-gray-400"
      >
        "We believe in learning without friction. This project is just the
        beginning."
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6">
        Have questions or want to contribute? Reach out to the team or check
        back later for community features, user dashboards, and more
        enhancements!
      </p>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer
      class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-400 py-6 border-t border-white/10 text-sm text-center"
    >
      &copy; 2025 Guide. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </body>
